Southeast Asian Nations agreed to set up a business council here
today to promote bilateral trade and investment.
</P>
<P>
An agreement was signed between the China Chamber of
International Commerce (CCIC) and the ASEAN Chambers of Commerce
and Industry (ASEAN-CCI) that states that the business council
will hold regular meetings to exchange economic, trade, and other
information.
