will play an important role in cooperation between China and ASEAN
and in promoting trade and investment between the two sides.
</P>
<P>
Setyanto Santosa, secretary-general of ASEAN-CCI, said that
both ASEAN and China enjoy the fastest economic growth in the
world and that there is vast potential for bilateral cooperation,
as the economies complement each other.
</P>
<P>
He said that a further strengthening of cooperation between
ASEAN and China is conducive to the prosperity and development of
the world's economy. 
