not long after. This unfortunate incident has caused a great deal
of suffering for his family and means large losses to them, ARATS
quoted a provincial department as saying.
</P>
<P>
Chen's family and the local fishermen were quite outraged by
the actions of the Taiwan forces, and urged Taiwan authorities to
bring the culprits to justice and compensate Chen's family for
their loss. 
