the DFA Commission on Filipino Overseas said she had already
conferred with several government agencies in Zambales, which will
help establish the centers.
</P>
<P>
DFA officials last month conducted talks with local officials
to work out the details for the establishment of migrant's
advisory and information network centers in Zambales, she said.
</P>
<P>
