agencies have assured that they will help in establishing the
centers in their areas starting September this year.
</P>
<P>
She added that the coordination of DFA with both local
governments and non-government organizations is the first phase in
the setting up of the centers which would bring migration-related
issues closer to the local residents.
</P>
<P>
The centers will educate overseas contract workers,
mail-to-order brides and migrants on issues such as illegal
recruitment and illegal matching of Filipino women with foreign
nationals, as well as the costs and benefits of social migration.
</P>
<P>
The official said that the DFA would also urge non-government
agencies to facilitate the setting up of such centers in the
future.  
