<HEADLINE> Sabotage Possibly Related to Blasts in Philippine </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MANILA, April 7 (Xinhua) -- Sabotage has not been ruled out as
the possible cause of two explosions that rocked an ammunition
depot at the Basa Airbase in Floridablanca, Pampanga, Saturday
afternoon, the newspaper Philippine Daily Inquirer said today.
